		<div class="comment-body"><p>I think it is important to carry both in a rural and urban environment.  In the rural environment, there are also less police and they are further away.  I live on a boundary between the two and can give several cases of problems in both parts of the state.</p>
<p>After the four cops were killed at the coffee shop south of me I started carrying 100%, up from about 75%.  I really would have a hard time living with myself if I was in a situation where I could have stopped something but wasn&#8217;t carrying that day.  How could I look into the widow or child&#8217;s eyes knowing I could and should have been prepared?  The odds are a million to one, but the consequences are horrific.</p>
